} 5. g3 {[%cal Yg2g3]} Be7 {[%cal Yf8e7]} 6. Bg2 {[%cal Yf1g2]} Ngf6 {[%cal
Yg8f6]} 7. Nxf6+ {[%csl Gf6][%cal Ye4f6]} Bxf6 {[%csl Gf6][%cal Ye7f6]} 8. -- {
